    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for reliable transportation with some cosmetic character. The exterior shows several noticeable scratches and a few small dents consistent with its age, though the paint still retains a decent shine. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and minor staining, and certain plastic trims show signs of use. Mechanically, it remains sound and has been regularly maintained, making it a practical choice for someone who prioritizes function over perfection.",
