    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in great shape, super reliable, and has been really well-loved over the years. It's the perfect dependable ride for someone who wants to just hop in and go. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home\u2014come see it for yourself and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
