    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 is a purist-spec example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-equipped limited-slip differential. The chassis provides telepathic feedback through its M-tuned suspension and staggered alloy wheels. To ensure long-term structural integrity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearings have been serviced. This driver-focused machine delivers a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline, offering a mechanical purity rarely found in modern performance cars.",
